      • getDataPointFromString

        protected IncomingDataPoint getDataPointFromString(TSDB tsdb,
                                                   String[] words)
        Converts the string array to an IncomingDataPoint. WARNING: This method does not perform validation. It should only be used by the Telnet style execute above within the error callback. At that point it means the array parsed correctly as per importDataPoint.
        Parameters:
        tsdb - The TSDB for encoding/decoding.
        words - The array of strings representing a data point
        Returns:
        An incoming data point object.
